import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Helmet } from 'react-helmet';
import GeneralBanner from '../Common/BannerParts/GeneralBanner';

class BasementRenovationsInToronto extends Component {
  static propTypes = {
  };

  state = {
  };

  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <Helmet>
          <title>AGM Basements | Basement Renovations in Toronto</title>
        </Helmet>
        <GeneralBanner title="Basement Renovations in Toronto" />
        <div className="container">
          <p>We are your premier basement contractors in Toronto, and we bring the highest level of quality, creativity, and craftsmanship to your basement project. At AGM Basements, we understand that contemporary basement designs focus on cost control and that is why our basement renovation packages come with professional basement drawings and designs at no extra cost. We also offer free estimates. Our commitment to customer satisfaction and timely completion of projects has seen us complete over 100 basements projects in Toronto having done more than 15 projects in 2017 alone.</p>

          <h3>Basement remodeling</h3>

          <p>Our basement builders in Toronto will skillfully design and remodel your basement space with your budget in mind. In our remodeling projects, we focus on creating versatile basement space that reflects your unique taste and lifestyle. This also ensures that your basement space serves a wide range of functions from home office, children's play area to home gym and bedroom. To achieve this, we have a team of highly skilled experts who work closely with clients to deliver what the clients want in their space, and this has enabled us to successfully complete projects of varied sizes from 2000sq./ft to 5000sq.ft.</p>

          <h3>Basement finishing</h3>

          <p>Our basement finishing services will transform your basement into a healthier and more comfortable living area by offering practical solutions for your basement including flooring, trimming, and moisture control. The result is a beautifully finished basement that suits your home and style. View our basement finishing services below and do not hesitate to schedule a free estimate.</p>

          <p>Painting – Our comprehensive painting package includes priming and painting tough areas like baseboards, ceilings, casing, and moldings.</p>

          <p>Flooring – Working with AGM Basements opens you to a vast range of basement flooring options, and we include the cost of premium laminate flooring in all our renovation packages.</p>

          <p>Bathroom and kitchen tiling – We have confidence in the quality of tiling we install in your basement, and that is why we offer a two-year unlimited warranty on all our installed tiling.</p>

          <p>Plumbing and electric – Our plumbers and electricians are knowledgeable and well equipped and will transform your basement space into a truly comfortable space through high-grade plumbing and electric services.</p>

          <p>Drywall installation – Our drywall hangers are highly skilled and well-versed with the latest methods and techniques to offer expert drywall hanging services. For a polished, look we also do Sheetrock installation.</p>

          <h3>Contact Us Today</h3>

          <p>Our basement renovation companies in Toronto uncover the unique aspect of your basement through exceptional basement renovations and pride ourselves on guaranteeing satisfaction to our customers. This means that they don't pay until they are completely satisfied with their basement.</p>

          <p>Call us today to know more about our basement services and schedule a free estimate for your home.</p>
        </div>
      </>
    );
  }
}

export default BasementRenovationsInToronto;
